headline: Charles River and CHDI Foundation Extend Multi-Decade Collaboration on Huntington’s Disease Research
summary: WILMINGTON, Mass., May 28, 2025--Charles River and CHDI announce an extension of their partnership, having worked together since 2005 to expedite therapies for Huntington's disease.
